Symbol.Script_3D:
! Designer Chair 10
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m=0 THEN END
PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL gs_resol
IF gs_shadow=0 THEN SHADOW OFF
IF GLOB_CONTEXT>20 and GLOB_CONTEXT<40 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m=1
ADD a/2,b/2,0
unID=1
HOTSPOT -a/2, -b/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -a/2, b/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT a/2, -b/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT a/2, b/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
hotspot -a/2+0.04, b/2-0.1515+(toth-0.0415)*TAN(10)+0.0674, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128: unID=unID+1 hotspot -a/2+0.04, b/2-0.1515+(toth-0.0415)*TAN(10)+0.0674, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3: unID=unID+1 hotspot -a/2+0.04, b/2-0.1515+(toth-0.0415)*TAN(10)+0.0674, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2: unID=unID+1
hotspot a/2-0.04, b/2-0.1515+(toth-0.0415)*TAN(10)+0.0674, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128: unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2-0.04, b/2-0.1515+(toth-0.0415)*TAN(10)+0.0674, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3: unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2-0.04, b/2-0.1515+(toth-0.0415)*TAN(10)+0.0674, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2: unID=unID+1
IF gs_full_edit=1 THEN
hotspot -a/2+0.12, -b/2+0.051, 0, unID, gs_seat_height, 1+128: unID=unID+1 hotspot -a/2+0.12, -b/2+0.051, -1, unID, gs_seat_height, 3: unID=unID+1 hotspot -a/2+0.12, -b/2+0.051, gs_seat_height, unID, gs_seat_height, 2: unID=unID+1
hotspot a/2-0.12, -b/2+0.051, 0, unID, gs_seat_height, 1+128: unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2-0.12, -b/2+0.051, -1, unID, gs_seat_height, 3: unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2-0.12, -b/2+0.051, gs_seat_height, unID, gs_seat_height, 2: unID=unID+1 ENDIF
ADD -0.01, -b/2, 0
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m=1 THEN ZH=gs_seat_height-0.011 MATERIAL gs_frame_mat ADDX -A/2 BRICK 0.02,B,.02 ADDZ 0.02 BRICK 0.02,0.02,ZH+0.13-0.02 ADDY B-0.02 BRICK 0.02,0.02,ZH+0.13-0.02 DEL 3 ADDX A/2-0.02 BRICK 0.02,B,.02 ADDZ 0.02 BRICK 0.02,0.02,ZH+0.13-0.02 ADDY B-0.02 BRICK 0.02,0.02,ZH+0.13-0.02 DEL 3 ADD -A/2+0.02,0,ZH+0.13-0.02 BRICK 0.09,0.02,0.02 ADD 0.09,0,-0.11 BRICK 0.02,0.02,0.13 ADDZ -0.02 BRICK A-0.22,0.02,0.02 ADD A-0.24,0,0.02 BRICK 0.02,0.02,0.13 ADD 0.02,0,0.11 BRICK 0.09,0.02,0.02 DEL 5 ADDY B-0.02 ADD -A/2+0.02,0,ZH+0.13-0.02 BRICK 0.09,0.02,0.02 ADD 0.09,0,-0.11 BRICK 0.02,0.02,0.13 ADDZ -0.02 BRICK A-0.22,0.02,0.02 ADD A-0.24,0,0.02 BRICK 0.02,0.02,0.13 ADD 0.02,0,0.11 BRICK 0.09,0.02,0.02 DEL 6 MATERIAL gs_seat_mat ADD -A/2+0.131,0,ZH+0.015 ROTY -90 RECT 0.1,B ADDZ -A+0.262 RECT 0.1,B DEL 3 ADD -A/2+0.015,0,ZH+0.131 RECT 0.1,B ADDX A-0.13 RECT 0.1,B DEL 2 ADD -A/2+0.12,0,ZH ROTX -10 ADDY 0.05 BLOCK A-0.24, B-0.24, 0.005 ADD -0.12,B-0.24,0 ROTX 90 ADDY 0.05 BLOCK A, 0.1, 0.005 ADDY 0.19+B*SIN(10)+0.01-0.145*COS(10) BLOCK A, TOTH-0.19-(0.03-SIN(10*0.03)), 0.005 DEL 7 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m=2 THEN SET MATERIAL gs_frame_mat RESOL gs_resol ZH=gs_seat_height-0.0112 ADDX -A/2+0.02 ADDY B ROTZ -90
! main section frame
ADDZ 0.010 ADDX 0.040 ROTY -90 ROTY 180
GOSUB 1 GOSUB 1
DEL 39 DEL 39 DEL 4
ADDY 0.020 ADDZ ZH+0.030 ROTY 90 CYLIND B, 0.010 ADDY A-0.06 CYLIND B, 0.010
! main section leather bits
SET MATERIAL gs_seat_mat
DEL 4
ADDX 0.010 ADDY 0.030 ADDZ 0.19+ZH BLOCK B-0.02, 0.070, 0.005 ADDY A-0.15 BLOCK B-0.02, 0.070, 0.005 ADDY -0.040 ADDZ -0.12 BLOCK B-0.02, 0.005, 0.100 ADDY -A+0.295 BLOCK B-0.02, 0.005, 0.100
! seat bit
SET MATERIAL gs_frame_mat DEL 7
ADDX B ADDZ ZH+.01 ADDY 0.110 ROTY -100 CYLIND 0.050, 0.010 ADDZ 0.050 SET MATERIAL gs_seat_mat CYLIND B-0.24, 0.010 ADDZ B-0.24 SET MATERIAL gs_frame_mat
PRISM_ 2,0.050, 0,0,974, 0.01,360,4074
ADDZ 0.050 ROTZ 90
ROTZ 90 ADDY -0.03 REVOLVE 2,90,1, 0,0.03,901, 0.01,360,4001 DEL 2
ADDZ 0.030 ADDX 0.030 ROTY 90
PRISM_ 2,A-0.3, 0,0,974, 0.01,360,4074
ADDZ A-0.30
ROTZ 90 ADDY -0.03 REVOLVE 2,90,1, 0,0.03,901, 0.01,360,4001 DEL 2
ADDX 0.030 ADDZ 0.030 ROTY 90
PRISM_ 2,0.050, 0,0,974, 0.01,360,4074
ADDZ 0.050 SET MATERIAL gs_seat_mat CYLIND B-0.24, 0.010 ADDZ B-0.24 SET MATERIAL gs_frame_mat CYLIND 0.050, 0.010 ADDZ 0.050 ADDY -0.005 ROTX 90 ROTZ -90 ADDX 0.050 SET MATERIAL gs_seat_mat BLOCK B-0.24, A-0.24, 0.005
DEL 22
! back bit
SET MATERIAL gs_frame_mat
ADDX B ADDZ ZH+0.01 ROTY -10 ADDX -B+0.15 ADDZ 0.010
PRISM_ 2,0.015, 0,0,974, 0.01,360,4074
ADDZ 0.015 SET MATERIAL gs_seat_mat CYLIND 0.100, 0.010 ADDZ 0.100 SET MATERIAL gs_frame_mat
CYLIND 0.19+B*SIN(10)+0.01-0.145*COS(10), 0.010 ADDZ 0.19+B*SIN(10)+0.01-0.145*COS(10) SET MATERIAL gs_seat_mat CYLIND TOTH-0.19-(0.03-SIN(10*0.03)), 0.010 ! ---------------
SET MATERIAL gs_frame_mat ADDZ TOTH-0.19-(0.03-SIN(10*0.03)) ROTZ 180
ROTZ 90 ADDY -0.03 REVOLVE 2,80,1, 0,0.03,901, 0.01,360,4001 DEL 2
ROTY -10 ADDX 0.028 ADDZ 0.028 ROTY -10 ROTZ -90 ROTX -90
ROTZ 90 ADDY -0.03 REVOLVE 2,90,1, 0,0.03,901, 0.01,360,4001 DEL 2
ADDX 0.030 ADDZ 0.030 ROTY 90
PRISM_ 2,A-0.08, 0,0,974+5, 0.01,360,4074+5
ADDZ A-0.08
ROTZ 90 ADDY -0.03 REVOLVE 2,90,1, 0,0.03,901, 0.01,360,4001 DEL 2
ADDX 0.030 ADDZ 0.030 ROTY 90 ROTZ 90
ROTZ 90 ADDY -0.03 REVOLVE 2,80,1, 0,0.03,901, 0.01,360,4001 DEL 2
DEL 16 SET MATERIAL gs_seat_mat ADDY A-0.02
CYLIND TOTH-0.19-(0.03-SIN(10*0.03)), 0.010 ADDZ -(0.19+B*SIN(10)+0.01-0.145*COS(10)) SET MATERIAL gs_frame_mat CYLIND 0.19+B*SIN(10)+0.01-0.145*COS(10),0.01
ADDZ -0.100 SET MATERIAL gs_seat_mat CYLIND 0.100, 0.010 ADDZ -0.015 SET MATERIAL gs_seat_mat
PRISM_ 2,0.015, 0,0,974, 0.01,360,4074
ROTX 180 ROTZ 90
ROTZ 90 ADDY -0.03 REVOLVE 2,90,1, 0,0.03,901, 0.01,360,4001 DEL 2
ADDX 0.030 ADDZ 0.030 ROTY 90
PRISM_ 2,0.1, 0,0,974, 0.01,360,4074
ADDZ A-0.18
PRISM_ 2,0.1, 0,0,974, 0.01,360,4074
ADDZ 0.100
ROTZ 90 ADDY -0.03 REVOLVE 2,90,1, 0,0.03,901, 0.01,360,4001 DEL 2
ADDZ 0.030 ADDX 0.030 ROTY 90 ADDY -0.010 ADDZ 0.015 SET MATERIAL gs_seat_mat BLOCK A-0.02, 0.005, 0.100 ADDZ 0.19+B*SIN(10)+0.01-0.145*COS(10)+0.1 BLOCK A-0.02, 0.005,TOTH-0.19-(0.03-SIN(10*0.03))
DEL 28 ENDIF
DEL 2
END
1: ! half main leg section
PRISM_ 2,B-0.08, 0,0,974, 0.01,360,4074 ADDZ B-0.05 ADDX -0.030 ROTY 90
ROTZ 90 ADDY -0.03 REVOLVE 2,90,1, 0,0.03,901, 0.01,360,4001 DEL 2 ROTY 180
PRISM_ 2,ZH+0.13, 0,0,974, 0.01,360,4074
ADDZ ZH+0.13 ROTZ 90 ROTZ 90 ADDY -0.03 REVOLVE 2,90,1, 0,0.03,901, 0.01,360,4001 DEL 2
ADDX 0.030 ADDZ 0.030 ROTY 90 SET MATERIAL gs_seat_mat CYLIND 0.070, 0.010 SET MATERIAL gs_frame_mat ADDZ 0.070 ELBOW 0.030, 90, 0.010 SET MATERIAL gs_seat_mat ADDX 0.030 ADDZ 0.030 ROTY 90 CYLIND 0.100, 0.010 SET MATERIAL gs_frame_mat ADDZ 0.100
PRISM_ 2,0.040, 0,0,974, 0.01,360,4074
ADDZ 0.040 ROTZ 180
ROTZ 90 ADDY -0.03 REVOLVE 2,90,1, 0,0.03,901, 0.01,360,4001 DEL 2
ADDX 0.030 ADDZ 0.030 ROTY 90
PRISM_ 2,A-0.34, 0,0,974, 0.01,360,4074
ADDZ A-0.34
ROTZ 90 ADDY -0.03 REVOLVE 2,90,1, 0,0.03,901, 0.01,360,4001 DEL 2
ADDZ 0.030 ADDX 0.030 ROTY 90
PRISM_ 2,0.040, 0,0,974, 0.01,360,4074
ADDZ 0.040 SET MATERIAL gs_seat_mat CYLIND 0.100, 0.010 ADDZ 0.100 SET MATERIAL gs_frame_mat ROTZ 180 ELBOW 0.030, 90, 0.010 ADDX 0.030 ADDZ 0.030 ROTY 90 SET MATERIAL gs_seat_mat CYLIND 0.070, 0.010 ADDZ 0.070 SET MATERIAL gs_frame_mat
ROTZ 90 ADDY -0.03 REVOLVE 2,90,1, 0,0.03,901, 0.01,360,4001 DEL 2
ADDX 0.030 ADDZ 0.030 ROTY 90
PRISM_ 2,ZH+0.13, 0,0,974, 0.01,360,4074
ADDZ ZH+0.13 ROTZ 90
ROTZ 90 ADDY -0.03 REVOLVE 2,90,1, 0,0.03,901, 0.01,360,4001 DEL 2
ADDX 0.030 ADDZ 0.030 ROTY 90 ROTZ 180
RETURN
Symbol.Script_2D:
! ====================================================================== ! SCALE ! ======================================================================
call "2dDetailLevel" parameters gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m, returned_parameters det2D
! --- 2D SYMBOL ----------------------------------------------------------------
if det2D = 1 then CALL "fa_ChairSymbol" PARAMETERS ALL gs_SymbolType_m=3 !! 1/200 if det2D = 2 then CALL "fa_ChairSymbol" PARAMETERS ALL gs_SymbolType_m=4 !! 1/100 if det2D = 4 then CALL "fa_ChairSymbol" PARAMETERS ALL !! Symbolic
if gs_SymbolType_m=1 OR gs_SymbolType_m=2 then if ABS(A-B) > EPS then unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 0,0, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 A,0, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 A,B, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 0,B, unID : unID = unID + 1 endif endif
! --- 1/50 --- if det2D = 3 then
PEN gs_cont_pen ! --- Minimal Space and Hotspots ---
CALL "fa_ChairSymbol" PARAMETERS ALL gs_SymbolType_m=0
! --- Symbol ---
add2 a/2,0
! --- Background Fill, Symbol --- FILL gs_fill_type POLY2_B 9, 2+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -A/2,0,1, -A/2+0.1,0,1, -A/2+0.1,0.05,1, A/2-0.1,0.05,1, A/2-0.1,0,1, A/2,0,1, A/2,B,1, -A/2,B,1, -A/2,0,1
LINE2 -A/2,B,A/2,B LINE2 -A/2,B,-A/2,0 LINE2 A/2,B,A/2,0 LINE2 -A/2+0.1,B,-A/2+0.1,0 LINE2 A/2-0.1,B,A/2-0.1,0 LINE2 -A/2+0.033,B-0.02,-A/2+0.033,0.02 LINE2 A/2-0.033,B-0.02,A/2-0.033,0.02 LINE2 -A/2,B-0.02,-A/2+0.033,B-0.02 LINE2 A/2,B-0.02,A/2-0.033,B-0.02 LINE2 -A/2,0.02,-A/2+0.033,0.02 LINE2 A/2,0.02,A/2-0.033,0.02 LINE2 -A/2,0,-A/2+0.1,0 LINE2 A/2-0.1,0,A/2,0 LINE2 -A/2+0.1,0.05,A/2-0.1,0.05 LINE2 -A/2+0.1,B-0.2,A/2-0.1,B-0.2 LINE2 -A/2+0.11,B-0.2,-A/2+0.11,0.05 LINE2 A/2-0.11,B-0.2,A/2-0.11,0.05
DEL 1
endif
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2 DLEV3D_DRAFT = 3
! Designer Chair 10 EPS=0.001
If gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 If gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 If gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_DETAILED then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2
gs_OrigoCentered = 0
dim stSymbolTypes[16] stSymbolTypes[ 1] = `Круглый` stSymbolTypes[ 2] = `Круглый со Спинкой` stSymbolTypes[ 3] = `Прямоугольный` stSymbolTypes[ 4] = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 1` stSymbolTypes[ 5] = `Трапециевидный` stSymbolTypes[ 6] = `Трапециевидный со Спинкой` stSymbolTypes[ 7] = `Криволинейный` stSymbolTypes[ 8] = `Криволинейный со Спинкой` stSymbolTypes[ 9] = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 3` stSymbolTypes[10] = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 2` stSymbolTypes[11] = `Круглый со Спинкой 2` stSymbolTypes[12] = `Круглый со Спинкой 3` stSymbolTypes[13] = `Криволинейный со Спинкой 2` stSymbolTypes[14] = `Криволинейный со Спинкой 3` stSymbolTypes[15] = `Детальный 1` stSymbolTypes[16] = `Детальный 2`
toth=(zzyzx-0.0415-gs_seat_height+0.0073)/COS(10)
Symbol.Script_VL:
HIDEPARAMETER ALL "A", "B", "zzyzx"
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.`
call "2dDetailLevel" parameters gs_detlevel_2D = gs_detlevel_2D, gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m, returned_parameters gs_detlevel_2D_m
if gs_detlevel_2D_m <> 4 then HIDEPARAMETER "gs_SymbolType" lock "gs_SymbolType", "gs_SymbolType_m" endif
call "fa_ChairSymbol" parameters all stSymbolTypes = stSymbolTypes
IF gs_cont_pen=0 THEN parameters gs_cont_pen=4 IF gs_fill_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=19
values "gs_resol" range [3,) values "a" range [0.35,) values "b" range [0.25,) values "gs_seat_height" range [b*SIN(10)+0.01, ZZYZX-0.3] values "zzyzx" range [gs_seat_height+0.3,)
if gs_detlevel_3D_m=1 then lock "gs_resol" hideparameter "gs_resol" endif if gs_detlevel_3D_m=0 then lock "gs_resol", "gs_shadow", "gs_full_edit" hideparameter "gs_resol", "gs_shadow", "gs_full_edit" endif
! --- Minimal Space ---
VALUES "MSFront" RANGE [0,) VALUES "MSSide" RANGE [0,) VALUES "MSRear" RANGE [0,)
Symbol.Script_UI:
UI_dialog `Параметры Стула`
ui_current_page gs_ui_current_page
dim tabTitles[4] tabTitles[1] = `Размеры и Минимальное Пространство` tabTitles[2] = `2D-отображение` tabTitles[3] = `3D-отображение и Покрытия` tabTitles[4] = `Характеристики`
dim tabIcons[4] tabIcons[1] = "uiTab_Dimension_flat(1)" tabIcons[2] = "uiTab_2DRepr_flat(1)" tabIcons[3] = "uiTab_3DRepr_flat(1)" tabIcons[4] = "uiTab_Descriptions_flat(1)"
FILE_DEPENDENCE "uiTab_Dimension_flat(1)" FILE_DEPENDENCE "uiTab_2DRepr_flat(1)" FILE_DEPENDENCE "uiTab_3DRepr_flat(1)" FILE_DEPENDENCE "uiTab_Descriptions_flat(1)"
iPageIDRoot =-1 iPageIDDimMinSpace = 1 iPageID2DRepresentation = 2 iPageID3DRepresentation = 3 iPageIDDescriptions = 4
pageStartY = 5 ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ !UI_PAGES ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
UI_PAGE iPageIDDimMinSpace, iPageIDRoot, tabTitles[1], tabIcons[1] gosub "dimMinSpacePage"
UI_PAGE iPageID2DRepresentation, iPageIDRoot, tabTitles[2], tabIcons[2] gosub "2DPage"
UI_PAGE iPageID3DRepresentation, iPageIDRoot, tabTitles[3], tabIcons[3] gosub "3DPage"
UI_PAGE iPageIDDescriptions, iPageIDRoot, tabTitles[4], tabIcons[4] gosub "descriptionPage"
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ end ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ !Subroutines ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "dimMinSpacePage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
x1 = 0 x2 = 228 y0 = pageStartY + 4
ui_outfield `Высота Сидения`, x1, y0, 168, 15 ui_infield "gs_seat_height", 169, y0 - 4, 90, 19
ui_separator 0, y0 + 21, 444, y0 + 21
pageStartY = pageStartY + 29
call "ui_chairs_minimalspace" parameters MSType = 1, ! MINSPACE_SIMPCHAIR MSSide = MSSide, pageStartY = pageStartY
return
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "2DPage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ call "ui_object_2DRepresentation" parameters iSymbolClass = 14, gs_SymbolType_m = gs_SymbolType_m, stSymbolTypes = stSymbolTypes, gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m, gs_2DSeat = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type = gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen = gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen = gs_back_pen, iFillListID = iPageID2DRepresentation
return
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "3DPage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ dim surfacesArray[2] surfacesArray[1] = "gs_frame_mat" surfacesArray[2] = "gs_seat_mat"
dim childFlagArray[2] childFlagArray[1] = 0 childFlagArray[2] = 0
call "ui_object_3DRepresentation" parameters bShowAnimation = 0, surfacesArray = surfacesArray, childFlagArray = childFlagArray, gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m, gs_resol = gs_resol, gs_shadow = gs_shadow, iSurfaceListID = iPageID3DRepresentation
return
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "descriptionPage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ dim stParamNames[16] stParamNames[1] = "gs_list_cost" stParamNames[2] = "gs_list_manufacturer" stParamNames[3] = "gs_list_note" stParamNames[4] = "gs_list_location" stParamNames[5] = "gs_list_accessories" stParamNames[6] = "FM_Type" stParamNames[7] = "FM_InventoryNumber" stParamNames[8] = "FM_SerialNumber" stParamNames[9] = "FM_ProductionYear" stParamNames[10] = "FM_ObjectWeight" stParamNames[11] = "FM_ObjectWeightUnit" stParamNames[12] = "gs_list_custom1" stParamNames[13] = "gs_list_custom2" stParamNames[14] = "gs_list_custom3" stParamNames[15] = "gs_list_custom4" stParamNames[16] = "gs_list_custom5"
call "ui_object_listing" parameters all listfieldID = iPageIDDescriptions, listFieldPosY = 0, listFieldHeight = 265, stDescHeader = "", stValueHeader = "", stParamNames = stParamNames return
